    <blockquote>
      <p><strong>Citation. </strong>Handler, A. Editorial: Thoughts About the National Evaluation of FIMR: Strategies for Evaluating Population-Based MCH Interventions. <em>Matern Child Health J</em> <strong>8, </strong>191–194 (2004). https://doi.org/10.1023/B:MACI.0000047417.38055.87</p>
      <p><strong>Abstract. </strong>NA</p>
    </blockquote>
